title: Episode 110: Feat. K. Camp
itunes:title: Episode 110: Feat. K. Camp
description:
Hip Hop artist K Camp sits with the ladies of Lip Service and discusses their worst injuries that occurred during sex, how to respond if they were being blackmailed with a sex-tape, and what they would do if someone they were dating had their bills in their ex’s name. K Camp even reveals the nickname he has for penis, as well as the most petty thing he’s done for revenge. Salute to K Camp for bringing gifts for the ladies….a giant bag of his own condoms.
